therefore  we consider a number of factors in establishing the allowance on a market by market basis  including historical collection experience  current economic trends  estimates of forecasted write offs  agings of the accounts receivable portfolio and other factors 
while we believe that the estimates we use are reasonable  actual results could differ from those estimates 
